  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>The hotel's restaurant serves up a buffet breakfast with hot options each morning. In the evening there's a lovely four- course meal with various choices and salad buffet. The hotel also holds a weekly gala dinner with an aperitivo where you can try the local Ladin specialties.</p>]]></cateringDescription>
