  <description><![CDATA[<p>Hotel La Plaza is a family-run hotel with a great location in the centre of <a data-udi="umb://document/f5a15898b6694ef6a1c755346a0e1ba8" href="/{localLink:umb://document/f5a15898b6694ef6a1c755346a0e1ba8}" title="Corvara &amp; Colfosco">Corvara</a>. The Boé gondola's about 300 metres away so it won’t take long before you’re out on the mountain each day.</p>
<h2>Ski-focused staff</h2>
<p>All the staff here are fantastic and will go out of their way to make your stay special. It’s run by Eduard, who’s a keen skier and always happy to share his tips with guests - be sure to ask him for his recommendations for the best area to ski, or where to go for a spot for lunch. With a great spot in the centre of Covara, the hotel has convenient access to the <a data-udi="umb://document/47c7f0773b104efb87f3357e7314f393" href="/{localLink:umb://document/47c7f0773b104efb87f3357e7314f393}" title="The Dolomites Ski Area">Dolomites Ski Area</a> - head up the nearby Boé gondola for access to the orange Sella Ronda route or head over to <a data-udi="umb://document/f5a15898b6694ef6a1c755346a0e1ba8" href="/{localLink:umb://document/f5a15898b6694ef6a1c755346a0e1ba8}" title="Corvara &amp; Colfosco">Colfosco</a> for cruisy blues and the green Sella Ronda route.</p>
<h2>Traditional Italian style</h2>
<p>The hotel’s decorated in a traditional style, so it's got a very welcoming feel to it.  Each of the rooms have all of the modern conveniences needed for a week in the Italian Dolomites, plus many of the rooms have a balcony so you can enjoy views over the resort and surrounding mountains. Before dinner, make the most of the sauna, solarium and whirlpool - it is a great way to unwind after a day of adventures.</p>
<h2>Dining</h2>
<p>The restaurant is the focal point and it’s a great place to come together at the end of the day to enjoy some warming food and share stories about your day. They serve up some great local specialties as well as dishes from across the Med. Each morning a hearty skiers buffet is served with local breads, homemade jams, dairy products and additional hot options. </p>
<h3>Exclusive to Inghams</h3>
<p>As a ski specialist tour operator we carefully select the very best accommodation in our resorts and package them with flights and transfers, so that you can make the most of your holiday. We have an exclusive agreement with Hotel La Plaza the only UK tour operator to package and sell holidays here - all the more reason to book with Inghams today!</p>]]></description>
